+------------------------+
|       FlaskApp         |
+------------------------+
| - pokemon_data: DataFrame  |  # Holds the Pokémon data loaded from the CSV file
+------------------------+
| + list_pokemon()         |  # Handles the GET request to list Pokémon with pagination
| + start_battle()         |  # Handles the POST request to start a battle between two Pokémon
| + get_battle_result()    |  # Handles the GET request to retrieve the result of a battle
+------------------------+

