                v
    +--------------------+         +--------------------+          +-------------------------+
    |   PokemonData      |         |      Database      |          |       BattleLogic        |
    +--------------------+         +--------------------+          +-------------------------+
    | - file_path: str   |         | - host: str        |          | - pokemon_data: DataFrame|
    |                    |         | - name: str        |          +-------------------------+
    | + load_data()      |         | - user: str        |          | + battle(pokemon_a,      |
    | # Loads and parses |         | - pass: str        |          |    pokemon_b, data)      |
    |   Pokémon data from|         +--------------------+          | # Simulates a battle     |
    |   a CSV file       |         | + save_battle_to_db()|        |   between two Pokémon,   |
    +--------------------+         | # Saves initial     |         |   calculates damage, and |
                                    |   battle data to DB|         |   determines the winner  |
                                    | + update_battle_in_db() |    +-------------------------+
                                    | # Updates battle    |
                                    |   status and result |
                                    |   in the database   |
